{"title":"心心向着斯大林","authors":["吕剑"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心向着斯大林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的大救星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的斯大林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年你的七十寿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献你什么好礼品？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说青青灵芝草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃了长生人不老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是真有灵芝草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千苦万难要去找！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马加鞭出北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日行千里一阵风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星夜赶过了玉门关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出时分到昆仑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山顶白雪白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山顶高又高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千寻万找难发现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间哪有灵芝草？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说王母有蟠桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃了长生人不老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是真有大蟠桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计要去找！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手化作翅膀飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风在我的翅边吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵的云彩染红霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵的雨珠朵朵的花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为找礼物腾云空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云中哪里有天宫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计难得到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里能有大仙桃？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地的珍珠光灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地的玛瑙红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地的珍宝数不上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到好礼心不安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑马不如骑闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里万里一眨眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高飞也不如骑闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我地球上走一转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矮处是湖水和平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高处是森林和大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上面好庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿海上面飘白帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上到青空下人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个地球全走遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找来找去难到手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶好的礼物那里有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听漫山遍野唱歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢喜的歌声好动听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声打破了国界和边境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口口声声唱着“斯大林”："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万道明霞当头照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水解冻冰雪消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你领着世界人民大翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你比那太阳还要亲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“克里姆宫发号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大帅统兵主意高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的大军打胜了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的堡垒垮台了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你的光明普照着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的言语暖人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和世界人民鱼和水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你童颜鹤发好青春！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千人万人象一人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千心万心心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人民的一片心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心向着斯大林！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要什么骑快马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山上寻灵芝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要什么进天宫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃林枝上偷蟠桃？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着灵芝草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着大仙桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的功业是永恒的碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的英名万万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，人类的大救星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，亲爱的斯大林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问今年你的七十寿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底献你什么好礼品？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“千人万人象一人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千心万心心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人民的一片心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心向着斯大林！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十二月十五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}